ZH: 我们终于登上了山顶，可以望见整个城市的景色。
EN: We finally reached the top of the mountain and could see the entire cityscape.

ZH: 在清晨的阳光下，我望见了一只小鹿在草地上悠闲地吃草。
EN: In the morning sunlight, I saw a deer leisurely eating grass in the meadow.

ZH: 爬上灯塔，可以望见远处的海洋和天空。
EN: Climbing up the lighthouse, you can see the ocean and sky in the distance.

ZH: 在山顶设立了观景台，游客可以望见壮丽的风景。
EN: A viewing platform was set up on the mountaintop, where tourists can see magnificent scenery.

ZH: 透过窗户，我可以望见院子里的花园。
EN: Through the window, I can see the garden in the yard.

ZH: 她站在高处，望见了整个城市的繁华景象。
EN: She stood at a high place and saw the bustling scene of the whole city.

ZH: 他站在山巅，望见了山下蜿蜒的小溪。
EN: He stood at the top of the mountain and saw the meandering stream below.

ZH: 登上高楼，可以望见城市的全景。
EN: Climbing up the high building, you can see the panoramic view of the city.

ZH: 从这里可以望见马路对面的公园。
EN: You can see the park across the street from here.

ZH: 来到这个山谷，你会望见美丽的瀑布。
EN: Coming to this valley, you will see a beautiful waterfall.

ZH: 她远远望见了海上波光粼粼的景象。
EN: She saw the sparkling sea from a distance.

ZH: 从废墟上方望见灯塔的光芒，给人一种希望的感觉。
EN: Seeing the light from the lighthouse above the ruins gives people a sense of hope.

ZH: 他站在山脊上，望见了群山连绵不绝的景象。
EN: Standing on the ridge, he saw the endless range of mountains.

ZH: 峡谷深处传来潺潺溪水声，可以望见远处的瀑布。
EN: The sound of gurgling streams came from the depths of the canyon, where you can see a distant waterfall.

ZH: 家庭聚会的时候，我望见了许多亲近的面孔。
EN: During the family gathering, I saw many familiar faces.

ZH: 站在阳台上，我望见了远处的海洋和蔚蓝的天空。
EN: Standing on the balcony, I saw the ocean and the blue sky in the distance.

ZH: 夜幕降临，她望见了星空中闪烁的星星。
EN: As night fell, she saw the stars twinkling in the sky.

ZH: 进入山林深处，你会望见许多野生动物。
EN: Going deep into the forest, you will see many wild animals.

ZH: 在这个高地，你可以望见日出和日落的美景。
EN: On this high ground, you can see the beautiful scenery of sunrise and sunset.

ZH: 站在山顶上，我望见了远处的村庄和稻田。
EN: Standing on the mountaintop, I saw the village and rice fields in the distance.
